00:45:00,739 --> 00:45:02,460
[SPEAKER_00] Neoštećen ono

899
00:45:02,460 --> 00:45:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] ko Biblija ko djela apostolska

900
00:45:04,360 --> 00:45:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] ludnica.

901
00:45:05,260 --> 00:45:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovi sad gledaju ono

902
00:45:07,000 --> 00:45:08,219
[SPEAKER_00] šta se to tamo događa

903
00:45:08,219 --> 00:45:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] neka ludnica.

904
00:45:08,960 --> 00:45:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] Počinje se stvarati odvajanje

905
00:45:11,699 --> 00:45:13,639
[SPEAKER_00] nema više tog iščekivanja.

906
00:45:13,639 --> 00:45:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] I gubi se lagano.

907
00:45:15,380 --> 00:45:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazimo da posebni sveci to iskušavaju

908
00:45:18,099 --> 00:45:20,480
[SPEAKER_00] počinju djelovati u tome.

909
00:45:20,820 --> 00:45:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz cijeli srednji vijek

910
00:45:22,920 --> 00:45:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] kroz renesansu

911
00:45:23,739 --> 00:45:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] cijelo vrijeme uvijek je bilo

912
00:45:24,920 --> 00:45:26,719
[SPEAKER_00] neko svjetlo koje je djelovalo

913
00:45:26,719 --> 00:45:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije bilo šire pokreta

914
00:45:28,340 --> 00:45:29,480
[SPEAKER_00] da ko je u prvoj crkvi

915
00:45:29,480 --> 00:45:31,760
[SPEAKER_00] da cijela crkva bude takva.

916
00:45:31,760 --> 00:45:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je puno milosti izgubljeno

917
00:45:35,500 --> 00:45:37,699
[SPEAKER_00] zato što crkva nije mogla to nositi.

918
00:45:39,139 --> 00:45:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo cagladati ravno, možda je bilo propusta,

919
00:45:41,639 --> 00:45:42,519
[SPEAKER_00] možda je moglo bolje.

920
00:45:42,519 --> 00:45:44,860
[SPEAKER_00] Možda smo izgubili djelomično ljubav,

921
00:45:44,860 --> 00:45:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] možda je bilo lakše reći

922
00:45:46,239 --> 00:45:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] odite na hodočašće u svetište pa ćete tamo moliti.

923
00:45:48,960 --> 00:45:51,139
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je bilo lakše, sigurno.

924
00:45:51,139 --> 00:45:53,320
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo se morali suočavati s time

925
00:45:53,320 --> 00:45:56,239
[SPEAKER_00] da molimo za nekoga on neozdravi.

926
00:45:56,239 --> 00:45:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] Šta onda? Šta onda reći?

927
00:45:58,619 --> 00:46:00,820
[SPEAKER_00] A, Bog hoće da budeš bolestan.

928
00:46:00,820 --> 00:46:03,019
[SPEAKER_00] A u cijeloj Bibliji samo ozdravljak.

929
00:46:03,019 --> 00:46:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] Svećenici su se tad

930
00:46:06,980 --> 00:46:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] i cijela crkva našli u teškoj situaciji.

931
00:46:09,440 --> 00:46:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] Odreagirali su kako su znali

932
00:46:11,559 --> 00:46:13,360
[SPEAKER_00] i Bogu hvala da su tako odreagirali

933
00:46:13,360 --> 00:46:15,340
[SPEAKER_00] jer kako su neki drugi odreagirali

934
00:46:15,340 --> 00:46:17,019
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo sačuvali tu milost.

935
00:46:17,019 --> 00:46:21,179
[SPEAKER_00] Francis McNutt prolazi i kroz protestante

936
00:46:21,179 --> 00:46:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] i što se sve događalo nakon reforme

937
00:46:23,500 --> 00:46:26,860
[SPEAKER_00] jedan paralelni put katoličke crkve

938
00:46:26,860 --> 00:46:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] i protestanskih crkava.

939
00:46:28,019 --> 00:46:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] Pravoslavnu crkvu ne spominje puno

940
00:46:30,219 --> 00:46:32,219
[SPEAKER_00] jer vjerojatno nijemo puno doticaja

941
00:46:32,219 --> 00:46:33,840
[SPEAKER_00] kod cijeli zapadni svijet

942
00:46:33,840 --> 00:46:35,780
[SPEAKER_00] što ne zna šta se događa na istoku.

943
00:46:35,780 --> 00:46:38,460
[SPEAKER_00] I dolazimo do toga

944
00:46:38,460 --> 00:46:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] da zadnji

945
00:46:40,019 --> 00:46:42,699
[SPEAKER_00] zadnji izdisaj

946
00:46:42,699 --> 00:46:43,800
[SPEAKER_00] pulsevi

947
00:46:43,800 --> 00:46:45,800
[SPEAKER_00] te službe ozdravljene

948
00:46:45,800 --> 00:46:46,960
[SPEAKER_00] na nekoj većoj razini

949
00:46:46,960 --> 00:46:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] se događaju po tome

950
00:46:49,039 --> 00:46:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] da

951
00:46:50,000 --> 00:46:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] ima naziv

952
00:46:52,440 --> 00:46:53,699
[SPEAKER_00] kraljevski dodira

953
00:46:53,699 --> 00:46:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju

954
00:46:55,840 --> 00:46:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] u Francuskoj i Engleskoj

955
00:46:57,579 --> 00:47:00,239
[SPEAKER_00] od negdje 1200 i neke

956
00:47:00,239 --> 00:47:01,940
[SPEAKER_00] do 1600 ili 1700

957
00:47:01,940 --> 00:47:02,719
[SPEAKER_00] te se ovisi

958
00:47:02,719 --> 00:47:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj državi pričamo

959
00:47:04,159 --> 00:47:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] se vjerovalo da samo kralj može ozdravljati.

960
00:47:06,500 --> 00:47:08,760
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su se događali

961
00:47:08,760 --> 00:47:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] tri ili četiri puta godišnje su bili ogromni skupovi

962
00:47:11,039 --> 00:47:11,820
[SPEAKER_00] gdje bi kralj

963
00:47:11,820 --> 00:47:12,900
[SPEAKER_00] tri i četiri dana

964
00:47:12,900 --> 00:47:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] doslovno dolazi pomo ljudi

965
00:47:14,539 --> 00:47:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] i on bi ih blagoslivljio.

966
00:47:15,639 --> 00:47:18,179
[SPEAKER_00] Tri i četiri dana je znalo trajati.

967
00:47:18,179 --> 00:47:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad razmislite ono

968
00:47:20,000 --> 00:47:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] doslovno ima zapisanih čudesa.

969
00:47:21,880 --> 00:47:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem da je dio njih

970
00:47:23,880 --> 00:47:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] možda i

971
00:47:25,079 --> 00:47:28,059
[SPEAKER_00] da se stvori veća priča o kraju.

972
00:47:28,059 --> 00:47:28,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem da je dio bio

973
00:47:28,940 --> 00:47:30,300
[SPEAKER_00] zbog ljudi koji su dolazili

974
00:47:30,300 --> 00:47:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] i vjerujem da se stvarno događalo.

975
00:47:31,619 --> 00:47:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ne bi ljudi dolazili.

976
00:47:32,960 --> 00:47:34,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi se moglo na taj način

977
00:47:34,820 --> 00:47:35,619
[SPEAKER_00] zavaravati ljude

978
00:47:35,619 --> 00:47:36,780
[SPEAKER_00] godinama godina.

979
00:47:36,780 --> 00:47:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znači 200-300 godina

980
00:47:37,980 --> 00:47:39,280
[SPEAKER_00] se to događalo.

981
00:47:39,280 --> 00:47:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čak je postojala jedna

982
00:47:41,000 --> 00:47:44,300
[SPEAKER_00] koje za stranjenje je to otišlo

983
00:47:44,300 --> 00:47:46,099
[SPEAKER_00] da je bilo vjerovanje

984
00:47:46,099 --> 00:47:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] da je sedmi sin u obitelji

985
00:47:47,880 --> 00:47:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] ima dar ozdravljanja.

986
00:47:49,440 --> 00:47:50,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ne šesti, ne osmi,

987
00:47:50,980 --> 00:47:52,320
[SPEAKER_00] nego sedmi i sin.

988
00:47:52,320 --> 00:47:55,219
[SPEAKER_00] I sad u Francuskoj to djeluje,

989
00:47:55,219 --> 00:47:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] a u Engleskoj skuže krahljevi.

990
00:47:57,039 --> 00:47:59,139
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sad ovi lječe,

991
00:47:59,139 --> 00:48:00,280
[SPEAKER_00] tamo nikom mi ne dolazi,

992
00:48:00,280 --> 00:48:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] meni je to dobro,

993
00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:01,780
[SPEAKER_00] prvo dođu,

994
00:48:01,780 --> 00:48:03,420
[SPEAKER_00] drugo postajem popularni,

995
00:48:03,420 --> 00:48:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] ipak je to ono,

996
00:48:04,400 --> 00:48:06,059
[SPEAKER_00] politički je bilo oportuno

997
00:48:06,059 --> 00:48:07,179
[SPEAKER_00] da ipak ono ljudi dolaze

998
00:48:07,179 --> 00:48:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] ozdravljaju ko njega,

999
00:48:07,960 --> 00:48:08,940
[SPEAKER_00] pa neće se priključiti

1000
00:48:08,940 --> 00:48:10,219
[SPEAKER_00] nekom koja hoće svrnuti.

1001
00:48:10,219 --> 00:48:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] I onda u Engleskoj

1002
00:48:11,460 --> 00:48:12,320
[SPEAKER_00] oni zabrane kažu

1003
00:48:12,320 --> 00:48:13,719
[SPEAKER_00] sedmi sin nema pravo,

1004
00:48:13,719 --> 00:48:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] nikom moli za ozdravljenje.

1005
00:48:15,480 --> 00:48:18,360
[SPEAKER_00] I to je to kraj priče.

1006
00:48:18,360 --> 00:48:19,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ostaje samo do krajlja,

1007
00:48:19,780 --> 00:48:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi protestanska reformacija,

1008
00:48:21,800 --> 00:48:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] čak aglinkanci ostavljaju to

1009
00:48:23,599 --> 00:48:24,719
[SPEAKER_00] sve dok ne dođe

1010
00:48:24,719 --> 00:48:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] nova ekipa iz Nilizanske,

1011
00:48:27,880 --> 00:48:29,139
[SPEAKER_00] nova kraljevska obitelj.

1012
00:48:29,139 --> 00:48:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su prvo ukinuli

1013
00:48:30,860 --> 00:48:32,199
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kad su vidjeli

1014
00:48:32,199 --> 00:48:33,780
[SPEAKER_00] u spisima šta se događalo,

1015
00:48:33,780 --> 00:48:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] ovo ne bi bilo loše,

1016
00:48:36,059 --> 00:48:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] zapalili ga za nas.

1017
00:48:37,360 --> 00:48:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su to organizirali,

1018
00:48:38,619 --> 00:48:39,679
[SPEAKER_00] ali ljudi su već zaborali

1019
00:48:39,679 --> 00:48:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] nakon djesto godina.

1020
00:48:40,539 --> 00:48:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] Izašlo je iz sjećanja naroda.

1021
00:48:43,320 --> 00:48:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] Nema više i nisu dolazili.

1022
00:48:45,460 --> 00:48:46,760
[SPEAKER_00] I to je bio kraj.

1023
00:48:46,760 --> 00:48:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je bio kraj

1024
00:48:48,480 --> 00:48:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] službe ozdravljanja u Engleskoj

1025
00:48:50,619 --> 00:48:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] kao takve,

1026
00:48:51,179 --> 00:48:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] koja je bila strukturno

1027
00:48:53,019 --> 00:48:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] organizirana od crkve.

1028
00:48:54,300 --> 00:48:55,139
[SPEAKER_00] Nema.

1029
00:48:55,139 --> 00:48:56,360
[SPEAKER_00] Gotovo.

1030
00:48:56,360 --> 00:48:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] U Francuskoj je ostalo

1031
00:48:57,599 --> 00:48:58,260
[SPEAKER_00] sve dok nisu

1032
00:48:58,260 --> 00:49:01,219
[SPEAKER_00] Luja 16. na Giljotinju ubili.

1033
00:49:01,219 --> 00:49:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] I njegov prethodnik je presao

1034
00:49:03,619 --> 00:49:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] zato što je se znalo

1035
00:49:04,519 --> 00:49:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] da on mora otići na ispovjed

1036
00:49:05,840 --> 00:49:06,699
[SPEAKER_00] prije nego što počne

1037
00:49:06,699 --> 00:49:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] sami taj obred.

1038
00:49:07,980 --> 00:49:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] A svi su znali da ima ljubavnicu

1039
00:49:09,500 --> 00:49:10,659
[SPEAKER_00] i da se ne želi ispovjedati.

1040
00:49:10,659 --> 00:49:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je to već ono,

1041
00:49:11,960 --> 00:49:13,099
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi su prestali dolaziti,

1042
00:49:13,099 --> 00:49:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] pa i on odustao svega toga.

1043
00:49:14,460 --> 00:49:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je Luja 16.

1044
00:49:15,599 --> 00:49:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] iako je bio svakakav organizirao,

1045
00:49:17,440 --> 00:49:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] ali eto,

1046
00:49:18,260 --> 00:49:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] ubrzo je umro,

1047
00:49:19,420 --> 00:49:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] tako da nije uspio

1048
00:49:20,880 --> 00:49:21,780
[SPEAKER_00] previše tog raditi.

1049
00:49:21,780 --> 00:49:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] I tu prestaje dolazi

1050
00:49:22,980 --> 00:49:24,719
[SPEAKER_00] Francuska revolucija,

1051
00:49:24,719 --> 00:49:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] prosvjetiteljstvo

1052
00:49:26,019 --> 00:49:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] i samim time

1053
00:49:26,960 --> 00:49:27,719
[SPEAKER_00] prosvjetiteljstvo

1054
00:49:27,719 --> 00:49:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] lagano počinje ulaziti

1055
00:49:28,739 --> 00:49:29,760
[SPEAKER_00] u crkvene strukture.

1056
00:49:31,139 --> 00:49:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] Čak svjetkatolička crkva,

1057
00:49:32,619 --> 00:49:34,219
[SPEAKER_00] ponome što vidim,

1058
00:49:34,219 --> 00:49:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu fala očuvala.

1059
00:49:36,199 --> 00:49:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] U protestantizmu

1060
00:49:37,599 --> 00:49:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] je često

1061
00:49:38,920 --> 00:49:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] zbog darova,

1062
00:49:40,159 --> 00:49:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] čudesa i ozdravljanja

1063
00:49:41,639 --> 00:49:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] dolazilo do šizmi novih,

1064
00:49:43,340 --> 00:49:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] do novih razdvajanja.

1065
00:49:45,320 --> 00:49:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo u Americi,

1066
00:49:46,159 --> 00:49:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] svi su bili maltene puritanci

1067
00:49:49,199 --> 00:49:51,139
[SPEAKER_00] pod jednom sličnom kapom

1068
00:49:51,139 --> 00:49:52,800
[SPEAKER_00] i onda dolaze dvojica ljudi

1069
00:49:52,800 --> 00:49:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] koji počinju navještat,

1070
00:49:53,900 --> 00:49:54,860
[SPEAKER_00] koji počinju

1071
00:49:54,860 --> 00:49:56,239
[SPEAKER_00] i to navještanje

1072
00:49:56,239 --> 00:49:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] počinju pratiti manifestacije,

1073
00:49:57,980 --> 00:49:58,719
[SPEAKER_00] ozdravljenja,

1074
00:49:58,719 --> 00:49:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] čak ne previše,

1075
00:49:59,920 --> 00:50:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali je počelo pratiti

1076
00:50:00,900 --> 00:50:02,360
[SPEAKER_00] i odmah ih se rješavaju.

1077
00:50:02,360 --> 00:50:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Kalvin i ekipa

1078
00:50:05,460 --> 00:50:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] su rekli ovako,

1079
00:50:06,559 --> 00:50:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] čudesa su bila

1080
00:50:08,460 --> 00:50:09,880
[SPEAKER_00] do smrti posljednjeg apostola.

1081
00:50:09,880 --> 00:50:11,519
[SPEAKER_00] Do tada je bilo.

1082
00:50:11,519 --> 00:50:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Iza toga ništa.

1083
00:50:12,539 --> 00:50:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] Iza toga samo Biblija.

1084
00:50:14,519 --> 00:50:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] Sola skriptura gotovo nema.

1085
00:50:15,880 --> 00:50:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] To što to piše u Bibliji

1086
00:50:17,239 --> 00:50:17,719
[SPEAKER_00] nema veze,

1087
00:50:17,719 --> 00:50:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo za to vrijeme.

1088
00:50:19,260 --> 00:50:21,440
[SPEAKER_00] To što piše Evanđeljom Marku,

1089
00:50:21,440 --> 00:50:22,820
[SPEAKER_00] pratit će i znakovi,

1090
00:50:22,820 --> 00:50:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] nema veze,

1091
00:50:23,619 --> 00:50:24,340
[SPEAKER_00] to je tamo.

1092
00:50:24,340 --> 00:50:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] I to je bio njihov službeni stav.

1093
00:50:25,880 --> 00:50:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je dan danas njihov službeni stav.

1094
00:50:28,039 --> 00:50:30,320
[SPEAKER_00] U protestantizmu imate

1095
00:50:30,320 --> 00:50:31,980
[SPEAKER_00] tri različite smjera.

1096
00:50:31,980 --> 00:50:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Imate jedan koji je onako negdje

1097
00:50:35,539 --> 00:50:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] na toj liniji,

1098
00:50:38,920 --> 00:50:39,699
[SPEAKER_00] nema ništa.

1099
00:50:39,699 --> 00:50:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su sve do 1994.

1100
00:50:42,019 --> 00:50:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] bila dva.

1101
00:50:43,519 --> 00:50:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] bila su dva protestantska smjera u Americi

1102
00:50:45,460 --> 00:50:47,059
[SPEAKER_00] koja su nastala iza suza strita.

1103
00:50:47,059 --> 00:50:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan pokret,

1104
00:50:49,099 --> 00:50:51,260
[SPEAKER_00] znači val obrnone koji se dogodio u Americi,

1105
00:50:51,260 --> 00:50:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] koji je povezan sa

1106
00:50:52,699 --> 00:50:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] karizmama i darovima duha svjetoga sa izljevima

1107
00:50:58,239 --> 00:50:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] koji se događaju.

1108
00:50:59,980 --> 00:51:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi je 1901.1.1. Nakon što papa Leo XIII. blagoslovi cijelo 20. stoljeće i moli za izljev duha.

1109
00:51:11,500 --> 00:51:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon što mu je blažena Jelena Gvera pisala pisma i potaknula ga da počne razmišljati o tome

1110
00:51:18,599 --> 00:51:25,139
[SPEAKER_00] da među katolicima je duh svet i nepoznate. Čak, ajde, moć je naš pa svi znaju iza oca,

1111
00:51:25,719 --> 00:51:30,300
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je spasitelj na svim slikama i pa znaju iza njega, ali o duhu svetom niko ne priča.

1112
00:51:30,300 --> 00:51:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] I on moli za izljev duha svetog na katoličku crkvu i na cijeli svijet i događa se fenomen da među protestantima kreće.

1113
00:51:39,860 --> 00:51:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo takvo iskustvo, 1.1.1901. se dolazi u Kansas City u Topeki i tamo kreće sve to u protestantskom pokretu.

1114
00:51:49,940 --> 00:51:59,699
[SPEAKER_00] Događa se iz te cijele priče, William Seymour 1908. godine doživljava slično iskustvo, pokreće pokret u Asusa Streetu

1115
00:51:59,699 --> 00:52:10,579
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo prvi put da u Americi i crnci i bijelici dolaze na isto mjesto, svi zajedno mole i širi se to iskustvo krštenja u duhu se širi cijelom Amerikom.

1116
00:52:10,579 --> 00:52:22,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dolazi do problema kad žele to napraviti kao nekako institucionalizirati, jer William je bio crnac, a većina drugih koji su vodili su bili bijelci.

1117
00:52:22,260 --> 00:52:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] Sad oni se stvore, skupština Božja se nazove denominacija, ali problem, većina su bijelci i donesu zakon, crnac ne smije biti voditelj bijelcu.

1118
00:52:32,579 --> 00:52:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] I svi crnci odu, osnoju svoju kongregaciju, bijelci i ostanu ovo i tek 1994. se te pentekostalne evanđeoske crkve opet spajaju i dolazi do pomirenja nekakvog.

1119
00:52:44,539 --> 00:52:46,519
[SPEAKER_00] Znači tamo je bio kaos cijeli.

1120
00:52:46,519 --> 00:52:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] Kod nas, koliko god naslov bio umalo ugašena milost, milost se nije ugasila.

1121
00:52:53,579 --> 00:52:58,159
[SPEAKER_00] Još uvijek je bilo dovoljno prostora da duh puše, crkva je dozvoljavala.

1122
00:52:58,159 --> 00:53:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] Šta god da se događalo, iako je bilo vjerojatno neki pogreški, moglo se na drugačiji nacijeli, ali crkva je dopuštala da duh puše.

1123
00:53:06,420 --> 00:53:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije utrnula do kraja.

1124
00:53:08,000 --> 00:53:13,340
[SPEAKER_00] I zato, nakon drugog vatikanskom koncila, dolazi do karizmatske obnove.

1125
00:53:13,340 --> 00:53:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, duh je čekao da propuše u katoličkoj crkvi, da prvo institucija kaže da.

1126
00:53:21,820 --> 00:53:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] Čudesa su za naše vrijeme.

1127
00:53:24,780 --> 00:53:32,840
[SPEAKER_00] Početak vatikanskom koncila, papa Ivan XXIII. moli za novu pedesetnicu, za nove duhove, da se omnove čudesa i znamenja.

1128
00:53:32,840 --> 00:53:44,219
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon završetka vatikanskom koncila, kad je presuđeno da, to je za naše vrijeme, nije samo za prvu crku, jer se moglo otići ovom linijom prvom protestanskom,

1129
00:53:44,219 --> 00:53:53,519
[SPEAKER_00] da je to bilo za prvo stoljeće, ubog straha od tjereza koji su se događale preko darova duha i karizmi, moglo se otići u tom smiru.

1130
00:53:53,519 --> 00:54:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] Al crkva, Bogu fala, je rekla da, to je za naše današnje vrijeme i danas nam je potrebno i duh zapuše jako.

1131
00:54:01,480 --> 00:54:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je onaj događaj koji sam vam spomenuo, dukein u 1967. na samom početku.

1132
00:54:05,920 --> 00:54:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] I dolazi do ponovnog oživljavanja manifestacija i čudesa koje su se događale i koje se dan danas događaju.

1133
00:54:13,480 --> 00:54:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] I duh sveti kao da nas je pripremo za sve ovo što se danas treba dogoditi.

1134
00:54:22,940 --> 00:54:30,699
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da nas je pripremo kroz to da je prvo sve počelo i prvo se najviše pričalo o oslobođenju od zlih duhova.

1135
00:54:30,699 --> 00:54:36,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kad gledate literaturu i teme o kojima se pričalo, to je bila tabu tema na početku.

1136
00:54:36,940 --> 00:54:43,219
[SPEAKER_00] Jer dolazkom novih duhova, novih manifestacija, to su bile nekako najglasnije priče.

1137
00:54:43,219 --> 00:54:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi do manifestacija zlodušnjih.

1138
00:54:45,820 --> 00:54:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, šta ćemo s time? Bavilo se s time.

1139
00:54:48,840 --> 00:54:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga Boga ozdravlja duh.

1140
00:54:52,559 --> 00:54:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga se počinje pisati o literaturi i pričati o unutarnjem ozdravljenju.

1141
00:54:57,159 --> 00:54:59,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ozdravljenju čovjekovih emocija.

1142
00:54:59,739 --> 00:55:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ozdravljenju čovjekove duše.

1143
00:55:01,559 --> 00:55:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Rana koje su stvorene kroz život.

1144
00:55:04,539 --> 00:55:06,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi do unutarnjeg ozdravljenja.

1145
00:55:06,739 --> 00:55:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog polako tu priprema.

1146
00:55:09,059 --> 00:55:11,820
[SPEAKER_00] Sada se prvi put nalazimo u trenutku

1147
00:55:11,820 --> 00:55:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] kada se u svijetu na karizimatskoj sceni katoličke crkve

1148
00:55:19,179 --> 00:55:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] počinje jako puno pričati o fizičkom ozdravljenju.

1149
00:55:24,980 --> 00:55:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] O tome da sve ovo što se događa,

1150
00:55:28,619 --> 00:55:33,179
[SPEAKER_00] sve ovo što se na neki način može objasniti kao

1151
00:55:33,179 --> 00:55:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] ma to je, ne znam šta,

1152
00:55:36,340 --> 00:55:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] jer došlo se do toga da određene struje u crkvi

1153
00:55:39,599 --> 00:55:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] počinju govoriti da sve i ono što je Isus radio,

1154
00:55:42,019 --> 00:55:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] da je to samo bilo nešto duhovo,

1155
00:55:44,440 --> 00:55:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] nešto su se oni omislili psihosomatski i tako.

1156
00:55:47,119 --> 00:55:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] To slovo postoji termin.

1157
00:55:49,019 --> 00:55:51,739
[SPEAKER_00] De mitologizacija.

1158
00:55:51,739 --> 00:55:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve što se dogodilo je mit, Isus je postoji,

1159
00:55:55,000 --> 00:55:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali on to nije činio stvarno.

1160
00:55:56,460 --> 00:55:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] Onaj čovjek kojem je ruha bila usakla,

1161
00:55:58,699 --> 00:56:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] njemu je ostala usahla,

1162
00:56:01,239 --> 00:56:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] ili mu nije opće bila, nek si on to omislio,

1163
00:56:03,300 --> 00:56:05,440
[SPEAKER_00] pa kad mu Isus rekao, pomakni ruku,

1164
00:56:05,440 --> 00:56:06,659
[SPEAKER_00] ona se pomaknula, jer eto,

1165
00:56:06,659 --> 00:56:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] psihi se promijenilo nešto.

1166
00:56:09,199 --> 00:56:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nestala je vjera u sama čudesa.

1167
00:56:14,500 --> 00:56:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] Sada se počinje u ovo našem krugu,

1168
00:56:18,239 --> 00:56:22,780
[SPEAKER_00] događa da se ono što se jedino ne može

1169
00:56:22,780 --> 00:56:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] objasniti nekim drugim jezikom,

1170
00:56:24,800 --> 00:56:28,159
[SPEAKER_00] da se dogodi da neko ko je u kolicima,

1171
00:56:28,159 --> 00:56:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ustane,

1172
00:56:29,739 --> 00:56:32,260
[SPEAKER_00] da neko ko ima ozbiljan zdravstveni problem,

1173
00:56:32,260 --> 00:56:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] da se ozdravi i da medicina to potvrdi.

1174
00:56:35,159 --> 00:56:37,719
[SPEAKER_00] I danas se počinje događati,

1175
00:56:37,719 --> 00:56:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] da se lagano počinje buditi svijest,

1176
00:56:39,920 --> 00:56:41,860
[SPEAKER_00] da je to moguće i počinje se događati

1177
00:56:41,860 --> 00:56:42,639
[SPEAKER_00] na nekim mjestima.

1178
00:56:42,639 --> 00:56:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo primjere i ovdje.

1179
00:56:45,539 --> 00:56:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] Znači imamo primjer, čuli smo svi za Šurkovac,

1180
00:56:48,139 --> 00:56:49,280
[SPEAKER_00] Međugorje,

1181
00:56:49,280 --> 00:56:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] mjesto u kojem se hrpa čudesa dogodila.

1182
00:56:52,699 --> 00:56:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali za sad je to i dalje na posebnim mjestima.

1183
00:56:56,539 --> 00:57:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] I dalje posebni ljudi, neki pojedinci,

1184
00:57:00,880 --> 00:57:02,179
[SPEAKER_00] nose pomazanje za to.

1185
00:57:02,179 --> 00:57:03,159
[SPEAKER_00] Jel neka mjesta?

1186
00:57:03,159 --> 00:57:06,019
[SPEAKER_00] I ako sam puno razmišljao o tome,

1187
00:57:06,019 --> 00:57:07,820
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je to tako?

1188
00:57:08,480 --> 00:57:11,159
[SPEAKER_00] I postoji jedno objašnjenje.

1189
00:57:11,159 --> 00:57:17,460
[SPEAKER_00] I došlo je u nenadanom razgovoru

1190
00:57:17,460 --> 00:57:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] s Marinom Restrepom.

1191
00:57:18,440 --> 00:57:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam s njim u trećem mjesecu

1192
00:57:20,300 --> 00:57:21,719
[SPEAKER_00] deset dana u PIH.

1193
00:57:21,719 --> 00:57:24,219
[SPEAKER_00] I u jednom razgovoru

1194
00:57:24,219 --> 00:57:28,280
[SPEAKER_00] bio jedan jako zanimljiv svećenik,

1195
00:57:28,280 --> 00:57:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] kapelan u Žepću,

1196
00:57:31,199 --> 00:57:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] Don Štefan Marković,

1197
00:57:32,400 --> 00:57:33,940
[SPEAKER_00] i on me postavljao puno pitanja.

1198
00:57:33,940 --> 00:57:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] On me postavljao na španjolskom,

1199
00:57:35,880 --> 00:57:37,800
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam onda ja na bade ono

1200
00:57:37,800 --> 00:57:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] da skužim šta je.

1201
00:57:39,460 --> 00:57:40,760
[SPEAKER_00] I ovo me jako zainteresiralo.

1202
00:57:40,760 --> 00:57:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] Sam skužio da se radi

1203
00:57:42,139 --> 00:57:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] o čudesvim ozdravljanjima i tako.

1204
00:57:43,760 --> 00:57:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ja njih pozavljam.

1205
00:57:45,239 --> 00:57:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo na engleski se prebaci

1206
00:57:46,920 --> 00:57:47,699
[SPEAKER_00] da i ja razumijem.

1207
00:57:47,699 --> 00:57:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže Marino

1208
00:57:49,539 --> 00:57:52,400
[SPEAKER_00] da je dobio otkrivenje od gospodina

1209
00:57:52,400 --> 00:57:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] zašto u Izraelu

1210
00:57:55,440 --> 00:57:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] kad je Ilija zazvao sušu,

1211
00:57:57,980 --> 00:57:59,820
[SPEAKER_00] čak to i Isus pominje,

1212
00:57:59,820 --> 00:58:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] nije Ilija otišao

1213
00:58:01,860 --> 00:58:03,639
[SPEAKER_00] kod nekoj Izraelke u Dovici,

1214
00:58:03,639 --> 00:58:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] nego otišao poganki.

1215
00:58:05,679 --> 00:58:07,219
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto za vrijeme Elizaja

1216
00:58:07,219 --> 00:58:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ilinog nasljednika

1217
00:58:09,480 --> 00:58:11,780
[SPEAKER_00] niko u Izraelu

1218
00:58:11,780 --> 00:58:14,739
[SPEAKER_00] nije bio ozdravljen od gube,

1219
00:58:14,739 --> 00:58:16,179
[SPEAKER_00] iako je bilo puno gubalaca,

1220
00:58:16,179 --> 00:58:18,179
[SPEAKER_00] nego namansirac isto Poganin.

1221
00:58:18,179 --> 00:58:20,679
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže,

1222
00:58:20,679 --> 00:58:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] ima jedan razlog

1223
00:58:22,039 --> 00:58:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] zašto se to dogodilo.

1224
00:58:23,579 --> 00:58:24,659
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan razlog

1225
00:58:24,659 --> 00:58:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] zašto u Nazare

1226
00:58:25,760 --> 00:58:27,139
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo svega par čuda.

1227
00:58:27,139 --> 00:58:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čak se Isus čudio

1228
00:58:29,000 --> 00:58:30,400
[SPEAKER_00] kako se to nije moglo dogoditi.

1229
00:58:30,400 --> 00:58:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] Njemu je to bilo zanimljivo.

1230
00:58:32,659 --> 00:58:34,360
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je pitao gospodina

1231
00:58:34,360 --> 00:58:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] i on mu je rekao,

1232
00:58:35,099 --> 00:58:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] izgubili su milost.

1233
00:58:37,039 --> 00:58:39,699
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže,

1234
00:58:39,699 --> 00:58:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] tad mi je sve postalo jasno.

1235
00:58:41,019 --> 00:58:42,639
[SPEAKER_00] Izgubili su.

1236
00:58:42,639 --> 00:58:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kao narod,

1237
00:58:43,920 --> 00:58:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] kao zajednica,

1238
00:58:45,400 --> 00:58:46,139
[SPEAKER_00] kao grupa,

1239
00:58:46,139 --> 00:58:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] Izraelci su u vrijeme

1240
00:58:47,460 --> 00:58:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ilije i Elizaja

1241
00:58:48,139 --> 00:58:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] izgubile milost

1242
00:58:48,960 --> 00:58:50,480
[SPEAKER_00] i Nazarečanini u vrijeme

1243
00:58:50,480 --> 00:58:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] Krista su izgubili milost.

1244
00:58:52,059 --> 00:58:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bilo dovoljno milosti.

1245
00:58:53,880 --> 00:58:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] Kao narod

1246
00:58:55,780 --> 00:58:57,179
[SPEAKER_00] su previše

1247
00:58:57,179 --> 00:58:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] ogradili u grijehu.

1248
00:58:58,380 --> 00:59:00,760
[SPEAKER_00] I sila nije mogla djelovati.

1249
00:59:00,760 --> 00:59:04,059
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Duh Sveti je gentleman.

1250
00:59:04,059 --> 00:59:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] Neće tamo gdje ga ne zovemo.

1251
00:59:05,800 --> 00:59:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] Izgubili smo milost.

1252
00:59:08,820 --> 00:59:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ono što se dogodilo

1253
00:59:10,059 --> 00:59:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] u zapadnom svijetu.

1254
00:59:10,900 --> 00:59:13,099
[SPEAKER_00] On mi onda priča

1255
00:59:13,099 --> 00:59:14,619
[SPEAKER_00] jednu priču koju sam čuo

1256
00:59:14,619 --> 00:59:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] o John Pridmora

1257
00:59:15,360 --> 00:59:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] u jednoj zajednici u Engleske.

1258
00:59:16,460 --> 00:59:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže,

1259
00:59:16,880 --> 00:59:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] to je najbolja karizmatska zajednica

1260
00:59:18,880 --> 00:59:19,559
[SPEAKER_00] koju poznajem.

1261
00:59:19,559 --> 00:59:20,699
[SPEAKER_00] New Dawn iz Engleske.

1262
00:59:20,699 --> 00:59:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1263
00:59:21,800 --> 00:59:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] najčišći su,

1264
00:59:22,519 --> 00:59:23,480
[SPEAKER_00] skroz su katolički,

1265
00:59:23,480 --> 00:59:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] nema ni milimetra.

1266
00:59:25,780 --> 00:59:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže,

1267
00:59:26,599 --> 00:59:27,280
[SPEAKER_00] idu,

1268
00:59:27,280 --> 00:59:28,780
[SPEAKER_00] pozovu ih u Afriku

1269
00:59:28,780 --> 00:59:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] na jednu duhovnu obnovu.

1270
00:59:31,519 --> 00:59:33,440
[SPEAKER_00] Sad oni dolaze tamo slijeću

1271
00:59:33,440 --> 00:59:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] i došekaju domaćin,

1272
00:59:36,199 --> 00:59:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] vozi ih prema hotelu.

1273
00:59:37,500 --> 00:59:38,780
[SPEAKER_00] Sad oni vide ono svaki

1274
00:59:38,780 --> 00:59:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] kilometar billboard

1275
00:59:40,380 --> 00:59:41,559
[SPEAKER_00] Miracle Rally.

1276
00:59:41,559 --> 00:59:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ono,

1277
00:59:42,420 --> 00:59:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] čudesa.

1278
00:59:43,039 --> 00:59:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] I datum.

1279
00:59:44,199 --> 00:59:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] I ovih pitao kao,

1280
00:59:45,039 --> 00:59:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] a šta je ovo?

1281
00:59:45,900 --> 00:59:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kad će ovo biti ovo?

1282
00:59:47,039 --> 00:59:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možda bi mi otišli.

1283
00:59:48,000 --> 00:59:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to ste vi.

1284
00:59:49,039 --> 00:59:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] Sad oni u šoku kao,

1285
00:59:51,119 --> 00:59:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] ne, to nismo mi.

1286
00:59:52,699 --> 00:59:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] Nama se ne događaju čudesa.

1287
00:59:54,579 --> 00:59:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] malo smo se zeslili,

1288
00:59:55,599 --> 00:59:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] šta ćemo sad?

1289
00:59:56,420 --> 00:59:57,119
[SPEAKER_00] Problem.

1290
00:59:57,119 --> 00:59:58,019
[SPEAKER_00] I ništa.

1291
00:59:58,019 --> 00:59:58,900
[SPEAKER_00] Oni, ono,

1292
00:59:58,900 --> 00:59:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] sad je gotovo,

1293
00:59:59,599 --> 01:00:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu povijeći.

1294
01:00:00,960 --> 01:00:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] Tu su već čovjekom u autu.

1295
01:00:02,579 --> 01:00:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] Idu.

1296
01:00:03,079 --> 01:00:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] Dolaze šator,

1297
01:00:04,460 --> 01:00:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] par tisuća ljudi.

1298
01:00:05,880 --> 01:00:06,699
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže sad,

1299
01:00:06,699 --> 01:00:06,920
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

1300
01:00:06,920 --> 01:00:07,760
[SPEAKER_00] oni imaju nagovor,

1301
01:00:07,760 --> 01:00:08,280
[SPEAKER_00] početak,

1302
01:00:08,280 --> 01:00:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] predstavljenje i sad.

1303
01:00:09,039 --> 01:00:10,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kreće molitva za ozdravljanje.

1304
01:00:10,639 --> 01:00:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] Sa mnom su u trenutku

1305
01:00:12,159 --> 01:00:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] da dogodi se

1306
01:00:13,579 --> 01:00:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] na svakom desetom susretu

1307
01:00:15,300 --> 01:00:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] neko čudo.

1308
01:00:15,800 --> 01:00:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kreće molitva.

1309
01:00:17,539 --> 01:00:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna osoba,

1310
01:00:19,380 --> 01:00:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] druga osoba.

1311
01:00:20,960 --> 01:00:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] tisuća čudesa.

1312
01:00:21,940 --> 01:00:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

1313
01:00:23,400 --> 01:00:24,340
[SPEAKER_00] svega par ljudi

1314
01:00:24,340 --> 01:00:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] koje je došlo

1315
01:00:25,019 --> 01:00:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] nije doživilo čudo,

1316
01:00:26,539 --> 01:00:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] a trebalo je,

1317
01:00:27,380 --> 01:00:28,079
[SPEAKER_00] a tražilo je.

1318
01:00:28,079 --> 01:00:30,099
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su bili

1319
01:00:30,099 --> 01:00:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] u totalnom šoku.

1320
01:00:31,420 --> 01:00:32,199
[SPEAKER_00] Nisu znali

1321
01:00:32,199 --> 01:00:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] ili to mogu,

1322
01:00:32,920 --> 01:00:33,739
[SPEAKER_00] šta se događa.

1323
01:00:34,340 --> 01:00:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ono,

1324
01:00:34,599 --> 01:00:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] ruka raste,

1325
01:00:35,659 --> 01:00:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] čovjek ostaje iz kolica,

1326
01:00:37,500 --> 01:00:38,260
[SPEAKER_00] ovi bacaju

1327
01:00:38,260 --> 01:00:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] štake,

1328
01:00:40,519 --> 01:00:41,800
[SPEAKER_00] žena progledala,

1329
01:00:41,800 --> 01:00:42,519
[SPEAKER_00] bila slijepa.

1330
01:00:42,519 --> 01:00:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] Čudo,

1331
01:00:43,039 --> 01:00:43,400
[SPEAKER_00] čudo,

1332
01:00:43,400 --> 01:00:43,719
[SPEAKER_00] čudo,

1333
01:00:43,719 --> 01:00:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu vjerovati.

1334
01:00:45,579 --> 01:00:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] I sad,

1335
01:00:47,300 --> 01:00:48,280
[SPEAKER_00] oni razmišljaju,

1336
01:00:48,280 --> 01:00:49,179
[SPEAKER_00] završilo je sve

1337
01:00:49,179 --> 01:00:50,760
[SPEAKER_00] i dalje su u šoku,

1338
01:00:50,760 --> 01:00:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] kažu,

1339
01:00:51,039 --> 01:00:52,579
[SPEAKER_00] vraćamo se u Englesku,

1340
01:00:52,579 --> 01:00:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo sad primili pomazanje,

1341
01:00:54,699 --> 01:00:56,179
[SPEAKER_00] idemo to nositi u Englesku,

1342
01:00:56,179 --> 01:00:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] idemo to nositi u Evropu,

1343
01:00:57,599 --> 01:00:59,719
[SPEAKER_00] idemo donosit evanđelje,

1344
01:00:59,719 --> 01:01:00,719
[SPEAKER_00] idemo navještati,

1345
01:01:00,719 --> 01:01:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] idemo,

1346
01:01:01,000 --> 01:01:02,260
[SPEAKER_00] čudesa će se događati,

1347
01:01:02,360 --> 01:01:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi će se obraćati,

1348
01:01:03,340 --> 01:01:05,179
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo sve gori.

1349
01:01:05,179 --> 01:01:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dođu u Englesku,

1350
01:01:07,880 --> 01:01:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] prvi susret,

1351
01:01:09,079 --> 01:01:10,420
[SPEAKER_00] ništa,

1352
01:01:10,420 --> 01:01:11,679
[SPEAKER_00] nula bodova.

1353
01:01:11,679 --> 01:01:13,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ide,

1354
01:01:13,320 --> 01:01:14,719
[SPEAKER_00] isti ljudi,

1355
01:01:14,719 --> 01:01:16,280
[SPEAKER_00] isti ljudi u Africi,

1356
01:01:16,280 --> 01:01:17,320
[SPEAKER_00] tišću čudesa,

1357
01:01:17,320 --> 01:01:18,340
[SPEAKER_00] isti ljudi u Englesku,

1358
01:01:18,340 --> 01:01:18,760
[SPEAKER_00] i ništa,

1359
01:01:18,760 --> 01:01:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] nula bodova nema.

1360
01:01:19,639 --> 01:01:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1361
01:01:21,119 --> 01:01:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] zapad je lagano izgubio milost.

1362
01:01:24,059 --> 01:01:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1363
01:01:25,079 --> 01:01:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] on isto jednom prilikom je rekao

1364
01:01:27,500 --> 01:01:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] da prije,

1365
01:01:28,980 --> 01:01:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] kad je tek počeo

1366
01:01:29,940 --> 01:01:32,340
[SPEAKER_00] misionarski rad,

1367
01:01:32,360 --> 01:01:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] i uvijek su mu govorili

1368
01:01:33,880 --> 01:01:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] kad ide u Afriku

1369
01:01:34,760 --> 01:01:35,139
[SPEAKER_00] i tako,

1370
01:01:35,139 --> 01:01:35,980
[SPEAKER_00] zemlja trećeg svijeta,

1371
01:01:35,980 --> 01:01:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] da se mora jako dobro pripremat

1372
01:01:38,019 --> 01:01:39,179
[SPEAKER_00] i molit zaštitu,

1373
01:01:39,179 --> 01:01:40,840
[SPEAKER_00] zato što tamo ima puno vraćeva,

1374
01:01:40,840 --> 01:01:42,739
[SPEAKER_00] puno poganštine,

1375
01:01:42,739 --> 01:01:43,400
[SPEAKER_00] puno svega.

1376
01:01:43,400 --> 01:01:44,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1377
01:01:44,159 --> 01:01:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] on bi se tad pripremao,

1378
01:01:45,400 --> 01:01:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi u strahu svaki put

1379
01:01:47,000 --> 01:01:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] kad bi je ušao u Afriku,

1380
01:01:48,119 --> 01:01:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] ili tako,

1381
01:01:48,519 --> 01:01:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] negdje ono,

1382
01:01:49,059 --> 01:01:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] hoći sad preživiti.

1383
01:01:50,440 --> 01:01:51,139
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1384
01:01:51,139 --> 01:01:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] došao bi tamo,

1385
01:01:52,039 --> 01:01:54,099
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi bi vidjeli da je Bog živ,

1386
01:01:54,099 --> 01:01:55,280
[SPEAKER_00] doživljeli bi nešto,

1387
01:01:55,280 --> 01:01:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] obratili bi se.

1388
01:01:56,000 --> 01:01:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno,

1389
01:01:57,619 --> 01:01:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] skroz.

1390
01:01:57,980 --> 01:01:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1391
01:01:59,000 --> 01:01:59,760
[SPEAKER_00] onda je shvatio

1392
01:01:59,760 --> 01:02:01,840
[SPEAKER_00] da puno više treba moliti

1393
01:02:01,840 --> 01:02:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] i puno više zaštite

1394
01:02:03,039 --> 01:02:04,679
[SPEAKER_00] kad ide u zapadni svijet.

1395
01:02:04,679 --> 01:02:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1396
01:02:05,739 --> 01:02:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] dođem u crkvu u Kanadi,

1397
01:02:07,019 --> 01:02:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] puna crkva,

1398
01:02:08,039 --> 01:02:08,639
[SPEAKER_00] sviju odijelima,

1399
01:02:08,639 --> 01:02:09,139
[SPEAKER_00] sve fino,

1400
01:02:09,139 --> 01:02:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] ja pričam,

1401
01:02:10,079 --> 01:02:11,179
[SPEAKER_00] vidim kak im se odbija.

1402
01:02:11,179 --> 01:02:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ne slušaju.

1403
01:02:13,500 --> 01:02:15,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1404
01:02:15,019 --> 01:02:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] shvatio je da ih je toliko obuzao

1405
01:02:18,019 --> 01:02:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] duh materializma,

1406
01:02:19,079 --> 01:02:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli zapad,

1407
01:02:20,599 --> 01:02:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] da je najvješta je gotovo nemoguća.

1408
01:02:23,460 --> 01:02:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] To isto i Michel Moran kaže.

1409
01:02:25,880 --> 01:02:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo bili u Rimu 2019.

1410
01:02:28,000 --> 01:02:29,300
[SPEAKER_00] Rekla je,

1411
01:02:29,300 --> 01:02:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] prije toga je govorila kao

1412
01:02:31,199 --> 01:02:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] vrata za evangelizaciju na zapadu se zatvaraju.

1413
01:02:35,000 --> 01:02:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] Gotovo je.

1414
01:02:36,500 --> 01:02:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] Još malo vremena postoji

1415
01:02:38,239 --> 01:02:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] gdje se može još šta uloviti.

1416
01:02:40,420 --> 01:02:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1417
01:02:41,599 --> 01:02:42,400
[SPEAKER_00] tako osjećamo.

1418
01:02:42,400 --> 01:02:43,579
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo bili 2019.

1419
01:02:43,579 --> 01:02:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1420
01:02:44,079 --> 01:02:45,280
[SPEAKER_00] vrata su zatvorene.

1421
01:02:45,280 --> 01:02:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] Par mjeseci nakon toga je došla

1422
01:02:47,940 --> 01:02:50,260
[SPEAKER_00] došla korona

1423
01:02:50,260 --> 01:02:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

1424
01:02:51,079 --> 01:02:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] tamo se više ne smije

1425
01:02:53,139 --> 01:02:55,159
[SPEAKER_00] evangelizirati na pravi način.

1426
01:02:55,159 --> 01:02:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1427
01:02:56,900 --> 01:02:59,360
[SPEAKER_00] ako govoriš protiv abortusa,

1428
01:02:59,360 --> 01:03:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] što je nauk katoličke crkve,

1429
01:03:01,519 --> 01:03:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] mogu te osuditi jer

1430
01:03:03,079 --> 01:03:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] napadaš druge,

1431
01:03:04,099 --> 01:03:04,840
[SPEAKER_00] govor mržnje.

1432
01:03:04,840 --> 01:03:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] Kažeš,

1433
01:03:06,420 --> 01:03:08,239
[SPEAKER_00] homoseksualizam je grijeh,

1434
01:03:08,239 --> 01:03:09,840
[SPEAKER_00] napad mržnje.

1435
01:03:09,840 --> 01:03:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš završiti u zatvoru.

1436
01:03:11,239 --> 01:03:12,480
[SPEAKER_00] Doslovno,

1437
01:03:12,480 --> 01:03:14,300
[SPEAKER_00] možeš završiti u zatvoru.

1438
01:03:14,300 --> 01:03:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] To se događa na zapadu.

1439
01:03:16,880 --> 01:03:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] Vrata se zatvaraju.

1440
01:03:17,980 --> 01:03:19,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ubi se milost.

1441
01:03:19,280 --> 01:03:20,360
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1442
01:03:20,360 --> 01:03:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] i zato,

1443
01:03:20,840 --> 01:03:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] što su se ljudi namjerno

1444
01:03:23,019 --> 01:03:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] odrekli,

1445
01:03:24,059 --> 01:03:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] zatvorili su sva vrata,

1446
01:03:25,940 --> 01:03:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] Bog,

1447
01:03:27,079 --> 01:03:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] džentlmen,

1448
01:03:27,639 --> 01:03:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] ne želi više.

1449
01:03:29,880 --> 01:03:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mi njega nećemo zazvat,

1450
01:03:32,119 --> 01:03:33,239
[SPEAKER_00] on neće,

1451
01:03:33,239 --> 01:03:34,800
[SPEAKER_00] on može kucat,

1452
01:03:34,800 --> 01:03:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] ali ako smo mi zatvorili vrata sami,

1453
01:03:36,719 --> 01:03:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] on neće ići protiv naše volje.

1454
01:03:39,980 --> 01:03:41,739
[SPEAKER_00] naša slobodna volja je to napravila.

1455
01:03:41,739 --> 01:03:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dalje postoji nada.

1456
01:03:45,099 --> 01:03:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dalje postoji nada,

1457
01:03:47,739 --> 01:03:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] ja mislim i da dalje postoje vrata,

1458
01:03:49,980 --> 01:03:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] bar kod nas,

1459
01:03:50,880 --> 01:03:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] da doživimo ono što su doživljavali

1460
01:03:54,699 --> 01:03:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] i u prvoj crkvi.

1461
01:03:56,619 --> 01:03:57,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ne na isti način.

1462
01:03:57,639 --> 01:03:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] Nećemo ići u to da ćemo mi postati

1463
01:03:59,519 --> 01:04:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] čista prva crkva.

1464
01:04:01,059 --> 01:04:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nego na naš način,

1465
01:04:02,599 --> 01:04:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] na novi način,

1466
01:04:03,340 --> 01:04:04,760
[SPEAKER_00] na način na koji duh sveti

1467
01:04:04,760 --> 01:04:06,219
[SPEAKER_00] želi zapuhati ovdje.

1468
01:04:06,219 --> 01:04:10,480
[SPEAKER_00] Jer crkva je ostavila otvorana vrata.

1469
01:04:10,480 --> 01:04:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] Po crkvi je još uvijek moguće

1470
01:04:13,460 --> 01:04:15,239
[SPEAKER_00] vratiti se nazad.

1471
01:04:15,239 --> 01:04:18,739
[SPEAKER_00] I to vidimo ponome,

1472
01:04:18,739 --> 01:04:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] što je papa govorio,

1473
01:04:20,440 --> 01:04:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] vidimo ponome što se događa u Africi,

1474
01:04:22,420 --> 01:04:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] što se dogodilo.

1475
01:04:23,559 --> 01:04:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] I dalje duh,

1476
01:04:24,760 --> 01:04:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] duh je još dalje živ,

1477
01:04:26,039 --> 01:04:27,280
[SPEAKER_00] duh i dalje privlače ljude.

1478
01:04:27,280 --> 01:04:29,820
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo oni koji su bili u Međugorju,

1479
01:04:29,820 --> 01:04:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] mogli su isto to primijetiti.

1480
01:04:31,380 --> 01:04:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] Još uvijek postoje,

1481
01:04:34,139 --> 01:04:36,760
[SPEAKER_00] u puku je ostalo to živo bilo

1482
01:04:36,760 --> 01:04:39,179
[SPEAKER_00] koje očekuje da Bog je živ

1483
01:04:39,179 --> 01:04:40,239
[SPEAKER_00] i da Bog djeluje.

1484
01:04:40,239 --> 01:04:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] I da Bog želi djelovati

1485
01:04:42,000 --> 01:04:43,219
[SPEAKER_00] na nevjerojatan način.

1486
01:04:43,219 --> 01:04:46,320
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko primjera

1487
01:04:46,320 --> 01:04:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] i koliko svjedočanstva ste sami čuli

1488
01:04:48,440 --> 01:04:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] da je neko otišao u Međugorje,

1489
01:04:50,559 --> 01:04:53,840
[SPEAKER_00] da je neko otišao u bilo koje svjetište

1490
01:04:53,840 --> 01:04:55,139
[SPEAKER_00] naše Ludbreg,

1491
01:04:55,460 --> 01:04:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] Marija Bistrica,

1492
01:04:56,420 --> 01:04:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] Podmilače,

1493
01:04:59,019 --> 01:05:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] da su doživili milost.

1494
01:05:01,239 --> 01:05:03,659
