[SPEAKER_00] Da jedemo tu večeru, tu gozbu.

1908
01:17:03,100 --> 01:17:07,760
[SPEAKER_00] Da jedemo puninu tih darova, a ne mrvice.

1909
01:17:08,880 --> 01:17:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] A Bog to želi.

1910
01:17:09,760 --> 01:17:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] Bog to daje.

1911
01:17:11,579 --> 01:17:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko smo toga primili?

1912
01:17:14,000 --> 01:17:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] Sad traži novi iskorak.

1913
01:17:18,239 --> 01:17:21,220
[SPEAKER_00] Mali, ne veliki.

1914
01:17:21,220 --> 01:17:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] Puno smo toga prošli.

1915
01:17:23,359 --> 01:17:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] Novi iskorak u vjeri.

1916
01:17:24,500 --> 01:17:26,100
[SPEAKER_00] Da je to moguće.

1917
01:17:26,100 --> 01:17:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] Da postanemo zajednica, mjesto, župa, država, biskupija koja iščekuje.

1918
01:17:34,699 --> 01:17:36,640
[SPEAKER_00] Prvoj crkvi su to očekivali.

1919
01:17:36,640 --> 01:17:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bilo hoće, neće, kako.

1920
01:17:39,460 --> 01:17:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] Očekuje se.

1921
01:17:40,460 --> 01:17:41,819
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je.

1922
01:17:41,819 --> 01:17:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] Osjeća se u zraku.

1923
01:17:43,119 --> 01:17:48,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ja isto osjećam u zraku, ali moramo svi osjećati da bi stvorili atmosferu

1924
01:17:48,760 --> 01:17:50,920
[SPEAKER_00] da kogod dođe da osjeti to.

1925
01:17:50,920 --> 01:17:56,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ista ona koja je osjetio brat kad je rekao vječno se spustila.

1926
01:17:56,680 --> 01:17:57,939
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je.

1927
01:17:57,939 --> 01:17:58,939
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto je drugačije.

1928
01:18:01,939 --> 01:18:05,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo doći do toga da nešto bude drugačije.

1929
01:18:05,279 --> 01:18:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] Da osjetimo dodir vječnosti ovdje.

1930
01:18:08,079 --> 01:18:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] Da možemo ustati i kliktati.

1931
01:18:12,159 --> 01:18:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ko što su kliktali svi u hramu kad su videli da je ovaj prohodo.

1932
01:18:17,840 --> 01:18:24,279
[SPEAKER_00] Da to bude ne jedno čudo u par godina, nego da bude na svaki dan.

1933
01:18:24,279 --> 01:18:25,939
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je moguće.

1934
01:18:25,939 --> 01:18:28,579
[SPEAKER_00] A mali korak.

1935
01:18:28,579 --> 01:18:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] A Bog zove.

1936
01:18:30,760 --> 01:18:35,760
[SPEAKER_00] Bog zove i zove da sjednemo na stol i da jedemo i da uživamo.

1937
01:18:35,760 --> 01:18:36,600
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

